               <p>First London Jury. - Before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>669. 
               
                  <persName id="t18300415-1-defend114" type="defendantName">
                     GEORGE 
                     EDWARDS
                  <interp inst="t18300415-1-defend114" type="surname" value="EDWARDS"></interp>
