             was indicted for <rs id="t18300415-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300415-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18300415-1-victim115" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Moody
                     <interp inst="t18300415-1-victim115" type="surname" value="Moody"></interp>
