                  , on the <rs id="t18300415-1-cd2" type="crimeDate">2nd of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-1-off1 t18300415-1-cd2"></join>, at the Inner Temple, and stealing 1 cloak, value 7l.; 1 coat, value 1l.; 1 pair of sugar-tongs, value 2s.; 1 umbrella, value 23s., and 1 carpet bag, value 3s., his property; 1 coat, value 2s., and 1 pair of boots, value 10s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-1-victim117" type="victimName">
                           Charles 
                           Strachan
                        <interp inst="t18300415-1-victim117" type="surname" value="Strachan"></interp>
